<P>
DMV COMPUTERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Where were the oversight and accountability that could have avoided the $44 
million squandered by the California Department of Motor Vehicles on a computer 
system (April 27) that showed scant promise of success even at its outset? Is 
it time to talk about privatizing the DMV? 
</P>
