representing Ventura, Ojai and Santa Paula and Santa Barbara County will 
participate in a question-and-answer forum sponsored by the League of Women 
Voters of Ventura County. Little House in Ojai, 111 W. Santa Ana St.; 7:30 p.m. 
Information: 646-1446. 
