representing Simi Valley, Moorpark and the Santa Rosa Valley will participate 
in a debate sponsored by the Citizens for a Safe and Scenic Simi Valley. Simi 
Valley City Council Chambers, 2929 Tapo Canyon Road; 7:30 to 9 p.m. 
Information: 522-6617. 
</P>
