</P>
<P>
 * The expression, "Don't ever embarrass me in public like that again," appears 
three times in the Bible. 
</P>
<P>
 * If the inventor of the wheel had patented it, he would today be worth more 
than $960 billion. 
</P>
<P>
 -- Mark Miller 
</P>
<P>
