</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
FUROR BUILDS OVER METHODS USED IN EXAMS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JEAN MERL, TIMES EDUCATION WRITER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
