</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 EMI Records' CEMA Distribution unit has named Gene Rumsey vice president of 
national accounts to help boost sales and marketing efforts with such major 
national chains as Musicland, Target, Blockbuster and Handelman. 
</P>
<P>
